Luna (c) Copyright 2009-2011 Ryan Zander
http://www.arabellan.org/projects/luna
A game community web application using the Django framework.

Installation
------------

1.  Install prerequisite libraries:
        - django-tagging
        - django-registration
        - django-pagination
        - python-markdown 2.1+

2.  Configure the settings.py file
3.  Construct the database (e.g. manage syncdb)
4.  Set basic site information (e.g. example.com/admin/sites)
5.  Configure Ventrilo support (e.g. example.com/admin/ventrilo/server/add)

How to use the 'update_ventrilo' command
----------------------------------------

Syntax: manage update_ventrilo HOST
Requirements:
    - HOST must be assigned to a Ventrilo Server in the admin console (see Installation step #5)

Update every 15 minutes via cron:
*/15 * * * * /path/to/project/manage.py update_ventrilo vent.example.com >> /log/update_ventrilo.log